title: Councilmember Sawant calls for halt to evictions, displacement at Chateau Apartments
description: Councilmember Kshama Sawant (District 3, Central Seattle), residents of the Chateau Apartments, clergy, local small business owners, and other supporters assemble at the Good Neighbor Caf to call on developers from Bellevue's Cadence Real Estate to meet with residents who will be evicted from their homes as a result of the developer's planned demolition.
